text: Poultry refers to domesticated birds kept by humans for their eggs, meat, feathers, or as pets. Poultry may also refer to: *Poultry farming *Poultry (office), the office in a medieval household responsible for the purchase and preparation of poultry *Poultry, London, a street in the City of London, United Kingdom **Poultry Compter, a former prison located on the street
title: Poultry (disambiguation)
